        We deliver strategic SEO with real impact for the Australian market, not empty promises.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Reasons Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
      {reasons.map((reason) => (
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-xl p-6 lg:p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100 hover:border-[#F57A18]/20 hover:-translate-y-1 cursor-pointer text-center">
